						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,4374109)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(634139); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=634139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227421" alt="Gene R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=634139)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(634139); return false;" >Gene R</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1569317874 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">24 Sep 2019 09:37</span>
